### Health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

### List products
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/products

### Create product
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sony WH-1000XM5",
  "store": "KSP",
  "product_url": "https://example.com/products/sony-wh1000xm5",
  "current_price": 1299.9,
  "target_price": 999.9,
  "currency": "ILS",
  "is_active": true
}

### Get product by id
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/products/1

### Update product
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "current_price": 949.9,
  "is_active": false
}

### Delete product
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/products/1
